  "title": "BUILDING CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR CUM DRIVER",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Scheduling the workers, and making sure instructions are carried out properly</p></li><li><p>Attend site meeting</p></li><li><p>Monitor, and keep track of the site work progress to ensure the waterproofing work is carried out in a quality and efficient manner.</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper documentation and reporting to the Senior Manager</p></li><li><p>Coordinate, communicate among team members, customers, and contractors and ensure all works are carried out according to approved drawing/specification</p></li><li><p>Provide on-site solutions during supervision works</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Min 3 years of experience in a supervising position</li><li>Able to work indenpendently</li><li>Able to read, understand, and work from technical drawing</li><li>Having a Building Construction Supervisors Safety (BCSS) Cert, Managing work at height,<strong> </strong>Class 3 Driving Licence, Confined space assessor.</li><li>Good communication skills, able to coordinate & liaise with people at all levels.</li><li>Able to work under tight schedules</li><li>Hard-working and keen to learn, with no criminal record</li><li>Team player and also able to work independently</li></ul></p>",
